# Improve Release Notes

## Purpose

Improve release note content based on review findings.

## Instructions

Use:

- Documentation Style Guide
- Release Note Specialist

Apply reviewer recommendations while preserving factual accuracy.

Requirements:

- Do not invent information.
- Maintain customer focus.
- Improve clarity.
- Improve consistency.
- Preserve original meaning.

## Inputs

Draft Release Notes

Review Findings

## Output

Improved Release Notes

Include a summary of changes made.
